overview:
TechColiseum - future International chain of start up accelerators, business centers and co-working spaces with Headquarters in Tampa Bay, Florida, USA.

TechColiseum - the international business space converted at the same time in a start up accelerator connected on a daily basis to a business community with business angels, investors, mentors and experts from around the world with plenty of co-working space and meeting rooms.

TechColiseum intents to create the perfect co-working space, and a great start up eco systems, which is intent to become like a micro Silicon Valleys, where entrepreneurial and creative individuals can meet, share, collaborate and co-create new projects and businesses, and also a place where investors can find a great opportunity to invest.
